        content: "AI is no longer exclusively for technology companies. A small independent business can today set up a chatbot to answer customer questions, automate social media content, or personalize sales emails. The question has shifted from 'should I use AI' to 'which tool should I choose to solve which specific problem.'\n\nThe most productive starting points are: basic chatbot systems for customer communication, language models for repetitive content production, generative AI tools for visual content drafts, and automated reporting systems for data analysis. The vast majority of these tools are available at accessible costs — often just a few dollars a month.\n\nThe critical point is to avoid the trap of seeing AI as a magic wand. Every tool solves a specific problem; define your problem clearly first, then seek the solution. At AuroraNova we offer our clients not only websites and branding but also consulting on which AI tools will make a genuine difference in their digital processes.",
