        content: "Aurora borealis — the Northern Lights — is one of the most mesmerizing visual phenomena nature has ever produced. Colors dancing across a dark sky: completely unpredictable yet perfectly harmonious. This natural symphony represents, for us, the essence of design: creativity and order, art and technology, chance and intention existing together.\n\n'Nova' means new in Latin, and in astronomical language describes a star that appears with a sudden burst of brightness. We see every new project this way: the moment our client emerges in the digital world with a sudden flash — visible, attention-commanding, and memorable.\n\nTo translate this philosophy into practice, we built a palette from aurora colors: deep night blue for trust and depth, purple for creativity and originality, gold for value and distinction, sage green for balance and sustainability. Across every touchpoint — from our profile to our portfolio — we aim to carry the atmosphere these colors create. Because a great brand should have a character that can be felt independently of its logo.",
